Welcome to Happy Pets!

 	A friendly and professional veterinary practice located in Polwarth, just south of Edinburgh City Centre.

Our friendly and dedicated staff consists of two veterinary surgeons, one nurse and three part-time receptionists. We believe in personalised care, not only for pets, but also for their owners. Our practice offers a variety of services to ensure the highest level of care for the pets of Edinburgh.


 	What we offer?
• General medicine and surgery
• Vaccination and full annual health checks
• Extended appointment times
• Neutering
• Dentistry
• Radiography
• Long term management of chronic conditions 
